Hindustan Petroleum Seeks to Buy Crude Oil for April Loading

-- B y   S h e r r y   S u
-- 
2011-02-17T12:22:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/hindustan-petroleum-seeks-to-buy-crude-oil-for-april-loading.html
Hindustan Petroleum Corp.,  India ’s
third-largest state refiner, is seeking to buy crude oil for
loading in April, according to a tender document obtained by
Bloomberg News.  Hindustan Petroleum operates two refineries, one in Mumbai
on the west coast of India and another in Visakhapatnam on the
east coast.  Details of the company’s requirements are as follows:  To contact the reporter on this story:
